  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KAFKA-ESQUE GIRLHOOD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Metamorph </strong>is a 3D story-driven dating sim with a horror theme, about growing up in a body that quickly becomes foreign to you. You play as a high-school girl who has begun to slowly, but steadily, turn into a <strong>twisted cockroach monster</strong>. With no signs of being able to reverse it, she sets out to score a date with her crush, all before her <strong>grotesque transformation</strong> is fully complete.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447550/extras/81cb1e9336a46a5402936e7b19b7bfb6.poster.avif?t=1768134943\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447550/extras/81cb1e9336a46a5402936e7b19b7bfb6.webm?t=1768134943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447550/extras/81cb1e9336a46a5402936e7b19b7bfb6.mp4?t=1768134943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HELL IS A TEENAGE GIRL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through social situations, interact with an unique cast of characters, and try your best to deal with your <strong>morphing body.</strong> As each day passes and your relationship with your crush unravels, <strong>your transformation spreads </strong>- The tendrils of your mind will begin playing tricks on you, making it harder and harder to conceal your condition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447550/extras/e6a42d78a97409f82dfeb55a9f818830.poster.avif?t=1768134943\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447550/extras/e6a42d78a97409f82dfeb55a9f818830.webm?t=1768134943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447550/extras/e6a42d78a97409f82dfeb55a9f818830.mp4?t=1768134943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A VERMINOUS WORLD</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Partial Voice Acting </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>17k+ Words of Dialogue</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5 Interactable NPC's</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Secret Side Quests</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 Different Endings</strong></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KAFKA-ESQUE GIRLHOOD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Metamorph </strong>is a 3D story-driven dating sim with a horror theme, about growing up in a body that quickly becomes foreign to you. You play as a high-school girl who has begun to slowly, but steadily, turn into a <strong>twisted cockroach monster</strong>. With no signs of being able to reverse it, she sets out to score a date with her crush, all before her <strong>grotesque transformation</strong> is fully complete.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447550/extras/81cb1e9336a46a5402936e7b19b7bfb6.poster.avif?t=1768134943\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447550/extras/81cb1e9336a46a5402936e7b19b7bfb6.webm?t=1768134943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447550/extras/81cb1e9336a46a5402936e7b19b7bfb6.mp4?t=1768134943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HELL IS A TEENAGE GIRL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through social situations, interact with an unique cast of characters, and try your best to deal with your <strong>morphing body.</strong> As each day passes and your relationship with your crush unravels, <strong>your transformation spreads </strong>- The tendrils of your mind will begin playing tricks on you, making it harder and harder to conceal your condition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447550/extras/e6a42d78a97409f82dfeb55a9f818830.poster.avif?t=1768134943\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"htt